   "postDate": "2026-06-10T14:58:56.653Z",
   "rawMarkdown": "My teammate and I have a problem.\nWe love our team name and think it's hilarious.\nOnnxlyFans 🤣🤣🤣\n\nHowever, we're afraid we might offend people and don't want to lose potentially great teammates. \n\nWe even made a github following the theme for casting auditions to join the team: \nhttps://github.com/Boladi888/K-NeuroGolf-OnnxlyFans-Auditions\n\nIf anyone thinks the team name is inappropriate, please let either of us know and we'll change the name immediately.\n\nOnnxly, we're just having fun 😝",
   "content": "<p>My teammate and I have a problem.\nWe love our team name and think it's hilarious.\nOnnxlyFans 🤣🤣🤣</p>\n<p>However, we're afraid we might offend people and don't want to lose potentially great teammates. </p>\n<p>We even made a github following the theme for casting auditions to join the team: \n<a href=\"https://github.com/Boladi888/K-NeuroGolf-OnnxlyFans-Auditions\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Boladi888/K-NeuroGolf-OnnxlyFans-Auditions</a></p>\n<p>If anyone thinks the team name is inappropriate, please let either of us know and we'll change the name immediately.</p>\n<p>Onnxly, we're just having fun 😝</p>",
